headline: FactSet Schedules Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Call
summary: NORWALK, Conn., May 29, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- FactSet (NYSE: FDS | NASDAQ: FDS), a global financial digital platform and enterprise solutions provider, today announced it will release its financial and operating results for the third quarter fiscal 2025, ending May 31, 2025, on Monday, June 23, 2025.
